</div>


    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">
        <strong>23 April 1952</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">Volume 499</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="debateContent">
                <div class="highlightedSearchTerms"></div>
                <div class="content-container">
<div class="content-item" id="contribution-310f9805-0c72-453f-bc9e-17e069240dde">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-310f9805-0c72-453f-bc9e-17e069240dde">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-310f9805-0c72-453f-bc9e-17e069240dde">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-310f9805-0c72-453f-bc9e-17e069240dde">
                Mr. John Parker
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-310f9805-0c72-453f-bc9e-17e069240dde" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-04-23/debates/1d6b3b8e-8dc7-4c53-97d3-98cfed6e6af7/NorthernRhodesiaAndNyasalandDelegates#contribution-310f9805-0c72-453f-bc9e-17e069240dde">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">(<em>by Private Notice</em>) asked the Secretary of State for the Colonies on what dates the invited African representatives from Northern Rhodesia and Nyasaland are returning to Central Africa and whether he will agree to prolong their stay at least until <span id="404" class="column-number" data-column-number="404"></span> Monday, 28th April, to allow Members of Parliament an opportunity to meet them.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-310f9805-0c72-453f-bc9e-17e069240dde" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-04-23/debates/1d6b3b8e-8dc7-4c53-97d3-98cfed6e6af7/NorthernRhodesiaAndNyasalandDelegates#contribution-310f9805-0c72-453f-bc9e-17e069240dde">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-7b72b93b-cfa4-415d-9146-92d34128271e">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-7b72b93b-cfa4-415d-9146-92d34128271e">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-7b72b93b-cfa4-415d-9146-92d34128271e">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-7b72b93b-cfa4-415d-9146-92d34128271e">
                Mr. Lennox-Boyd
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7b72b93b-cfa4-415d-9146-92d34128271e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-04-23/debates/1d6b3b8e-8dc7-4c53-97d3-98cfed6e6af7/NorthernRhodesiaAndNyasalandDelegates#contribution-7b72b93b-cfa4-415d-9146-92d34128271e">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">As hon. Members will have heard with regret, the delegates from the African Representative Council of Northern Rhodesia and the African Protectorate Council of Nyasaland have declined the invitation of Her Majesty's Government to remain in London to attend the Conference on Closer Association in Central Africa. Arrangement had therefore been made by their Governments for them to return home on 24th and 25th April respectively. If, however, there is a general desire in the House that hon. Members should have a chance of discussion with them, I am assured that the two Governors would be willing to arrange for them to stay here for two or three days for this purpose.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7b72b93b-cfa4-415d-9146-92d34128271e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-04-23/debates/1d6b3b8e-8dc7-4c53-97d3-98cfed6e6af7/NorthernRhodesiaAndNyasalandDelegates#contribution-7b72b93b-cfa4-415d-9146-92d34128271e">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-b8f13549-73c4-45d4-934c-a0cfde8e00ae">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-b8f13549-73c4-45d4-934c-a0cfde8e00ae">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-b8f13549-73c4-45d4-934c-a0cfde8e00ae">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-b8f13549-73c4-45d4-934c-a0cfde8e00ae">
                Mr. J. Griffiths
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-b8f13549-73c4-45d4-934c-a0cfde8e00ae" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-04-23/debates/1d6b3b8e-8dc7-4c53-97d3-98cfed6e6af7/NorthernRhodesiaAndNyasalandDelegates#contribution-b8f13549-73c4-45d4-934c-a0cfde8e00ae">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">May I impress upon the Minister the importance of consulting the two Governors immediately and indicating what I am sure is the general view of the House—these Africans have come here and we know they are opposed to federation—that it is of the utmost importance that no impression should be given that any attempt has been made to prevent them from stating their case to Members of this House and to the country?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b8f13549-73c4-45d4-934c-a0cfde8e00ae" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-04-23/debates/1d6b3b8e-8dc7-4c53-97d3-98cfed6e6af7/NorthernRhodesiaAndNyasalandDelegates#contribution-b8f13549-73c4-45d4-934c-a0cfde8e00ae">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-b0532e83-c573-4c54-a148-664850d8f31b">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-b0532e83-c573-4c54-a148-664850d8f31b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-b0532e83-c573-4c54-a148-664850d8f31b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-b0532e83-c573-4c54-a148-664850d8f31b">
                Mr. Lennox-Boyd
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-b0532e83-c573-4c54-a148-664850d8f31b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-04-23/debates/1d6b3b8e-8dc7-4c53-97d3-98cfed6e6af7/NorthernRhodesiaAndNyasalandDelegates#contribution-b0532e83-c573-4c54-a148-664850d8f31b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">That is why I gave the answer in that form.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b0532e83-c573-4c54-a148-664850d8f31b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-04-23/debates/1d6b3b8e-8dc7-4c53-97d3-98cfed6e6af7/NorthernRhodesiaAndNyasalandDelegates#contribution-b0532e83-c573-4c54-a148-664850d8f31b">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
