<p class="">With respect, may I call your attention, Mr. Speaker, to the fact that the conference only began an hour ago and that the first intimation we had of this change of policy by Her Majesty's Government was in a reply to a supplementary question put to the Minister? Therefore, I feel that the fact that the conference has begun and the policy is already in operation makes it a very urgent matter.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
