            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-1116cc7c-6df4-480c-b143-4ee86d2dc7d6">
                Mr. I. J. Pitman
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1116cc7c-6df4-480c-b143-4ee86d2dc7d6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
